1
00:00:38,679 --> 00:00:39,039
Take a look at this

2
00:00:41,240 --> 00:00:42,240
That's pretty interesting

3
00:00:42,320 --> 00:00:44,640
Sir, this is from the Qianlong period

4
00:00:45,280 --> 00:00:47,200
I bought this off a descendant

5
00:00:47,200 --> 00:00:47,840
of the Yehenara clan.

6
00:00:48,920 --> 00:00:49,719
If you like it,

7
00:00:49,920 --> 00:00:51,079
I'll sell it to you cheap.

8
00:00:51,560 --> 00:00:53,000
Dad, these are all fake.

9
00:00:53,640 --> 00:00:54,200
No, no, no.

10
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:56,079
I'm scoring a bargain here.

11
00:00:56,600 --> 00:00:56,960
Yeah.

12
00:01:04,480 --> 00:01:06,560
You said it's from the Qianlong period,

13
00:01:08,079 --> 00:01:09,159
But this glaze looks way too new.

14
00:01:09,519 --> 00:01:10,799
If it truly is from the Qianlong period,

15
00:01:11,120 --> 00:01:12,599
would the glaze flake off with a scratch?

16
00:01:13,879 --> 00:01:15,599
Well, with the passage of time,

17
00:01:15,599 --> 00:01:16,840
it tends to do that.

18
00:01:17,359 --> 00:01:18,519
This jade transmits light unevenly,

19
00:01:18,879 --> 00:01:19,719
and there are bubbles inside.

20
00:01:20,920 --> 00:01:22,480
Ancient jade pendants were hand-polished.

21
00:01:23,040 --> 00:01:23,840
How could there be bubbles?

22
00:01:24,959 --> 00:01:25,760
All right, all right, enough.

23
00:01:25,840 --> 00:01:26,799
I'm not selling it. I'm not selling it.

24
00:01:27,200 --> 00:01:27,760
Put it down.

25
00:01:28,680 --> 00:01:29,120
Not for sale.

26
00:01:32,560 --> 00:01:32,760
Give it to me, give it to me.

27
00:01:32,959 --> 00:01:33,719
You little punk.

28
00:01:34,200 --> 00:01:35,879
When'd you learn that skill?

29
00:01:37,560 --> 00:01:38,400
I don't know either.

30
00:01:39,040 --> 00:01:40,719
It just came out before I could think.

31
00:01:42,599 --> 00:01:44,680
See if anything here is worth money.

32
00:01:45,760 --> 00:01:46,159
Fake.

33
00:01:46,359 --> 00:01:46,920
Fake.

34
00:01:47,079 --> 00:01:47,680
This one's fake too.

35
00:01:47,840 --> 00:01:48,719
And this one.

36
00:01:49,040 --> 00:01:49,680
These are all fake.

37
00:01:49,879 --> 00:01:50,760
All fake.

38
00:01:51,359 --> 00:01:52,640
What about my copper coins?

39
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:56,640
CEO of Sky Roc Entertainment, Zhu Zipeng,

40
00:01:56,640 --> 00:01:58,040
is past the Bronze Sparrow Club incident,

41
00:01:58,280 --> 00:01:59,719
and is publicly preparing a new shoot.

42
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:19,360
I went to finish that bastard off.

43
00:02:19,680 --> 00:02:20,759
You went to finish him off?

44
00:02:21,080 --> 00:02:21,680
You couldn't even get near him,

45
00:02:21,680 --> 00:02:22,879
and you got hauled off to the Police.

46
00:02:23,080 --> 00:02:24,080
So we just let him get away with it?

47
00:02:26,560 --> 00:02:27,719
You can't take down Zhu Zipeng.

48
00:02:28,879 --> 00:02:29,319
Leave it to me.

49
00:02:30,599 --> 00:02:31,319
You...

50
00:02:32,080 --> 00:02:32,960
You said before

51
00:02:34,080 --> 00:02:34,919
that I owed your sister.

52
00:02:35,360 --> 00:02:36,960
I absolutely hate owing anyone anything.

53
00:02:43,120 --> 00:02:44,479
I've got an important business meeting.

54
00:02:44,800 --> 00:02:45,879
A project worth hundreds of millions.

55
00:02:46,159 --> 00:02:47,120
It's all pocket change.

56
00:02:47,599 --> 00:02:49,039
I'll take you to a movie after this.

57
00:02:53,680 --> 00:02:54,400
Miss Zhu.

58
00:03:00,599 --> 00:03:02,400
I didn't expect you to be so beautiful.

59
00:03:03,000 --> 00:03:04,400
Then I'll get straight to the point.

60
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:06,000
There's something you should know

61
00:03:06,159 --> 00:03:07,439
that I need to make clear in advance.

62
00:03:07,639 --> 00:03:08,319
As for me,

63
00:03:08,560 --> 00:03:10,840
my one flaw is I attract too many women.

64
00:03:11,080 --> 00:03:11,840
You need to be obedient.

65
00:03:12,159 --> 00:03:13,800
Jealousy is a huge taboo for a wife.

66
00:03:14,840 --> 00:03:15,919
You're that confident

67
00:03:16,080 --> 00:03:17,159
that I'll definitely marry you?

68
00:03:17,800 --> 00:03:18,840
If you don't marry into our family,

69
00:03:19,479 --> 00:03:21,599
my dad won't fund Sky Roc Entertainment.

70
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:23,000
Isn't your family counting on

71
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:24,080
trading you for that money?

72
00:03:24,719 --> 00:03:25,439
She doesn't have to marry.

73
00:03:25,960 --> 00:03:26,439
I'll invest.

74
00:03:28,120 --> 00:03:29,159
And who the hell are you?

75
00:03:29,960 --> 00:03:30,560
Get out of here.

76
00:03:31,199 --> 00:03:33,520
Sheng Yuanzhou, from Prosperity Group.

77
00:03:36,319 --> 00:03:37,479
Young Master Sheng from Prosperity Group.

78
00:03:37,960 --> 00:03:38,759
My apologies, my apologies.

79
00:03:39,400 --> 00:03:39,919
Let's go.

80
00:03:40,240 --> 00:03:41,639
Let him cool off here by himself.

81
00:03:42,800 --> 00:03:43,120
Oh, right.

82
00:03:43,560 --> 00:03:44,479
Tell your dad for me,

83
00:03:44,960 --> 00:03:46,240
I don't care about your family's money,

84
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:48,240
or you.

85
00:03:52,199 --> 00:03:53,960
Mr. Sheng, thank you for today.

86
00:03:54,479 --> 00:03:55,199
If you hadn't been there,

87
00:03:55,199 --> 00:03:56,439
I wouldn't have known what to do.

88
00:03:56,879 --> 00:03:57,639
My parents always say

89
00:03:57,639 --> 00:03:59,240
a married daughter is like spilled water.

90
00:03:59,520 --> 00:04:01,280
Before I'm married off, they always want

91
00:04:01,560 --> 00:04:02,520
to squeeze some value out of me.

92
00:04:03,680 --> 00:04:05,479
Thank you so much for today.

93
00:04:07,039 --> 00:04:08,000
Honestly, even if I hadn't come,

94
00:04:09,919 --> 00:04:11,000
you could've handled him.

95
00:04:14,080 --> 00:04:15,039
Then why did you

96
00:04:15,039 --> 00:04:16,160
come to my rescue again today?

97
00:04:16,439 --> 00:04:17,480
Because I don't want to wait anymore.

98
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:19,879
I'll be blunt.

99
00:04:20,519 --> 00:04:22,120
I'm actually here to lend you a hand.

100
00:04:22,839 --> 00:04:23,439
I looked into it.

101
00:04:24,160 --> 00:04:25,079
The major projects that turned

102
00:04:25,600 --> 00:04:27,240
Sky Roc Entertainment into a

103
00:04:27,240 --> 00:04:28,000
leading entertainment company

104
00:04:28,399 --> 00:04:30,240
were all personally led by you.

105
00:04:31,120 --> 00:04:33,000
But your parents have son preference,

106
00:04:33,439 --> 00:04:34,839
In the end, your family's assets

107
00:04:35,120 --> 00:04:36,600
can only go to Zhu Zipeng.

108
00:04:37,480 --> 00:04:39,519
You're just a pawn in a Marriage alliance.

109
00:04:43,720 --> 00:04:45,240
No matter how they treat me,

110
00:04:45,519 --> 00:04:46,720
they're still my family.

111
00:04:47,279 --> 00:04:48,480
We're bound by blood.

112
00:04:49,319 --> 00:04:50,959
Stabbing family in the back

113
00:04:51,240 --> 00:04:52,000
isn't something I can do.

114
00:04:52,240 --> 00:04:52,680
Is that so?

115
00:04:53,160 --> 00:04:55,120
Then why did you upload

116
00:04:55,920 --> 00:04:57,800
that rainy-day secret video online?

117
00:05:04,639 --> 00:05:05,680
Don't look so shocked.

118
00:05:06,680 --> 00:05:08,319
As Prosperity Group's heir,

119
00:05:09,000 --> 00:05:10,480
I at least have that much capability.

120
00:05:11,519 --> 00:05:13,079
You posted that secret video online

121
00:05:14,279 --> 00:05:15,279
not to hurt me,

122
00:05:15,839 --> 00:05:17,079
but to use me

123
00:05:17,439 --> 00:05:19,360
to dig up Zhang Xiaoyu's death again.

124
00:05:19,639 --> 00:05:20,399
But digging it up again,

125
00:05:20,399 --> 00:05:21,720
what good does it do you?

126
00:05:22,519 --> 00:05:24,720
I thought it over and finally realized,

127
00:05:25,279 --> 00:05:27,360
you're after the real killer, Zhu Zipeng.

128
00:05:28,600 --> 00:05:29,519
So this is what you meant by

129
00:05:30,079 --> 00:05:32,000
not stabbing family in the back, huh?

130
00:05:34,680 --> 00:05:36,480
Even if I want to bring my brother down,

131
00:05:37,279 --> 00:05:38,480
then, Young Master Sheng,

132
00:05:39,040 --> 00:05:40,560
why would you help me?

133
00:05:41,160 --> 00:05:43,040
You know the Bronze Sparrow Club incident.

134
00:05:43,439 --> 00:05:44,240
He crossed me,

135
00:05:44,720 --> 00:05:46,199
so I'm definitely not letting him off.

136
00:05:49,199 --> 00:05:51,199
Young Master Sheng, can you dance?

137
00:05:52,160 --> 00:05:55,079
Interested in being my dance partner?

138
00:05:55,839 --> 00:05:57,519
The venue is Bronze Sparrow Club.

139
00:06:39,560 --> 00:06:40,959
My brother has a secret computer.

140
00:06:41,160 --> 00:06:42,399
It contains years' worth of videos

141
00:06:42,639 --> 00:06:43,759
of him using Bronze Sparrow Club

142
00:06:43,759 --> 00:06:45,079
to conduct sexual bribery.

143
00:06:45,519 --> 00:06:47,360
Behind the booth is his private room.

144
00:06:47,959 --> 00:06:49,360
The computer should be in the safe.

145
00:06:49,759 --> 00:06:50,360
In a bit, I'll handle

146
00:06:50,360 --> 00:06:51,879
distracting the door guards for you.

147
00:06:52,319 --> 00:06:54,160
The rest depends on your skills.

148
00:06:55,240 --> 00:06:56,600
I came prepared too.

149
00:07:04,319 --> 00:07:05,279
Who is this?

150
00:07:07,639 --> 00:07:09,560
Sis, your new pet?

151
00:07:10,199 --> 00:07:10,879
Yeah.

152
00:07:11,319 --> 00:07:12,160
Even more handsome than you.

153
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:13,800
Handsome or not...

154
00:07:14,160 --> 00:07:15,240
we'll only know once he takes it off.

155
00:07:16,720 --> 00:07:18,360
What's the fun in revealing it so soon?

156
00:07:19,480 --> 00:07:20,120
So protective.

157
00:07:23,639 --> 00:07:24,800
Don't tell me it's because of him

158
00:07:25,040 --> 00:07:25,959
that you ruined the blind date

159
00:07:25,959 --> 00:07:27,240
Mom set up for you?

160
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:28,920
I'm telling you,

161
00:07:29,360 --> 00:07:30,439
once a woman hits thirty,

162
00:07:30,439 --> 00:07:31,680
she's past her prime.

163
00:07:33,439 --> 00:07:35,279
I think Sis is in her prime.

164
00:07:36,399 --> 00:07:37,319
And incredibly irresistible.

165
00:07:39,079 --> 00:07:40,839
There's no place for a Simp to speak here.

166
00:07:41,319 --> 00:07:42,480
Young Master Zhu is only half right.

167
00:07:43,040 --> 00:07:43,959
I don't just lick.

168
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:45,600
I also bite.

169
00:07:46,399 --> 00:07:47,360
Wanna try it, Young Master Zhu?

170
00:07:47,639 --> 00:07:48,480
You have a death wish!

171
00:07:55,120 --> 00:07:56,759
I'd hate for you to bite someone else.

172
00:07:58,720 --> 00:07:59,240
Forget it.

173
00:07:59,800 --> 00:08:01,240
I'm done being the third wheel here.

174
00:08:01,839 --> 00:08:02,759
But I'm warning you,

175
00:08:03,639 --> 00:08:04,319
you'll have to give Mom an explanation

176
00:08:04,800 --> 00:08:05,879
sooner or later.

177
00:08:06,439 --> 00:08:07,480
Mind your own business.

178
00:08:08,360 --> 00:08:08,800
I'm leaving.

179
00:08:10,600 --> 00:08:12,480
I look forward to your performance later.

180
00:08:40,440 --> 00:08:41,960
This bastard.

181
00:09:07,639 --> 00:09:09,080
I smelled a stench.

182
00:09:09,360 --> 00:09:10,480
Turns out a rat snuck in.

183
00:09:10,919 --> 00:09:11,600
Get him!

184
00:09:24,159 --> 00:09:24,679
Somebody!

185
00:09:25,200 --> 00:09:25,960
Somebody, come!

186
00:09:27,519 --> 00:09:28,320
Someone, help!

187
00:09:29,919 --> 00:09:30,639
Forget people.

188
00:09:31,720 --> 00:09:32,919
Even a god couldn't save you.

189
00:09:33,399 --> 00:09:35,039
Because I'm executing divine justice.

190
00:09:36,600 --> 00:09:37,159
Spare me!

191
00:09:38,080 --> 00:09:38,759
This time...

192
00:09:39,600 --> 00:09:41,000
...let's see how you escape.

193
00:09:43,879 --> 00:09:45,600
Sky Roc Entertainment's CEO, Zhu Zipeng,

194
00:09:45,759 --> 00:09:48,279
was arrested by the Police for charges

195
00:09:48,480 --> 00:09:49,559
like tax evasion and illegal fundraising.

196
00:09:50,039 --> 00:09:50,720
Investigations found that the

197
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:53,200
Prosperity Group worker who killed herself

198
00:09:53,440 --> 00:09:55,039
was also assaulted by Zhu Zipeng.

199
00:09:55,720 --> 00:09:57,600
Sky Roc Entertainment stock price plunged.

200
00:09:57,919 --> 00:09:59,799
falling as much as 10 percent that day.

201
00:10:00,120 --> 00:10:01,120
Prosperity Group's stock price

202
00:10:01,240 --> 00:10:02,799
has returned to pre-scandal levels.

203
00:10:03,440 --> 00:10:03,960
Experts state that

204
00:10:04,279 --> 00:10:06,320
more accurate forecasts come next week.

205
00:10:07,440 --> 00:10:08,360
In a few days, Sky Roc Entertainment

206
00:10:09,080 --> 00:10:10,960
will hit limit down for consecutive days.

207
00:10:11,679 --> 00:10:12,519
Then in a few more days,

208
00:10:13,159 --> 00:10:14,639
we can start buying it at a low price.

209
00:10:15,399 --> 00:10:17,360
Despite a small setback,

210
00:10:18,200 --> 00:10:19,519
you still did a pretty good job.

211
00:10:21,120 --> 00:10:22,799
You've finally shown some growth.

212
00:10:24,399 --> 00:10:25,480
Thank you for the praise, Father.

213
00:10:27,320 --> 00:10:29,480
I hope you keep up this momentum,

214
00:10:29,679 --> 00:10:32,000
so I can consider

215
00:10:32,480 --> 00:10:34,559
making you the Sheng family's heir.

216
00:10:40,200 --> 00:10:41,120
I'll keep working hard.

217
00:10:43,639 --> 00:10:44,360
Also,

218
00:10:45,159 --> 00:10:47,960
take Lin Siqi to try her engagement dress.

219
00:10:48,440 --> 00:10:49,399
Your marriage

220
00:10:49,679 --> 00:10:51,080
needs to be put on the agenda.

221
00:10:51,320 --> 00:10:51,879
Yes, Father.

222
00:10:54,799 --> 00:10:56,840
Sheng Shizhong didn't let Sheng Yuanzhou

223
00:10:57,159 --> 00:10:58,600
become Prosperity Group's heir.

224
00:10:59,720 --> 00:11:00,240
Why?

225
00:11:01,159 --> 00:11:02,559
He's his only biological son.

